OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FA Cumbria hospital has been forced to
OL,8,Fmake urgent changes after an
OL,9,Finspection found failings in its
OL,10,Fmental health care.
OL,12,FNorth Cumbria Integrated Care NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust (NCIC) says it has
OL,14,Ftaken 'immediate action' after
OL,15,Freceiving an enforcement notice from
OL,16,Fthe Care Quality Commission (CQC).
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FIt follows an unannounced inspection
OL,8,Fof the Emergency Department (ED) at
OL,9,Fthe Cumberland Infirmary in February
OL,10,F2026, where inspectors found a number
OL,11,Fof concerns."
OL,13,FThe inspection team then revisited in
OL,14,FMarch 2026 for a further review.
OL,16,FThe main areas of concern were around
OL,17,Fthe care of mental health patients in
OL,18,Fthe Emergency Department and oversight
OL,19,Fof patients in the waiting area.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FAs a result, the Trust received formal
OL,8,Fnotification of a Section 31, which
OL,9,Fgrants the CQC the ability to impose
OL,10,Fconditions on a provider's
OL,11,Fregistration.
OL,13,FEarlier this year, it was announced
OL,14,Fthat the NCIC was one of the worst
OL,15,Fservices in the country and would be
OL,16,Fput into a recovery programme as the
OL,17,Fgovernment planned to tackle the issue.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,8,F"failure has been tolerated for too
OL,9,Flong", as he named five NHS trusts
OL,10,Fthat will be placed in the 'NHS
OL,11,FIntensive Recovery programme'.
OL,13,FFollowing the enforcement notice from
OL,14,Fthe health regulator, the trust said
OL,15,Fit recognises it needs to improve
OL,16,Furgent care facilities at the
OL,17,FCumberland Infirmary.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FThe trust said it will now have a
OL,8,Fhealthcare assistant or nurse in the
OL,9,Femergency department waiting room to
OL,10,Foversee patients while they wait, and
OL,11,Fwill make sure mental health risk
OL,12,Fassessments are carried out when
OL,13,Fpatients arrive.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FCommenting on the CQC's action, Gill
OL,8,FFindley, Chief Nurse at NCIC said: "We
OL,9,Fknow that all of our colleagues come
OL,10,Fto work to do a good job for their
OL,11,Fpatients everyday so naturally it is
OL,12,Fvery disappointing and concerning to
OL,13,Freceive an enforcement notice from the
OL,14,FCQC.
OL,26,@pD@dOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,F"The most important thing is to take
OL,8,Fimmediate action to resolve the issues
OL,9,Fraised and to make sure they are
OL,10,Fresolved on a permanent basis rather
OL,11,Fthan a temporary fix. The team in the
OL,12,FEmergency Department have responded
OL,13,Freally well to the notice and have
OL,14,Fbeen determined to make the necessary
OL,15,Fimprovements.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,F"We recognise that we need to improve
OL,8,Four urgent care facilities at the
OL,9,FCumberland Infirmary. The ED was
OL,10,Foriginally designed to accommodate
OL,11,F30,000 patients a year and we are now
OL,12,Fseeing around 70,000.
OL,14,F"That is why we are investing #4m into
OL,15,Four urgent and emergency care services
OL,16,Fto help us to stream less urgent cases
OL,17,Fto the most appropriate place and free
OL,18,Fup ED for the critically ill patients.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1779459069
OL,3,C'Urgent changes' imposed at Cumbria
OL,4,Chospital after mental health care
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,F"It is important that we provide our
OL,8,Fstaff with the facilities and staffing
OL,9,Flevels they need to enable them to
OL,10,Fprovide the best possible care to our
OL,11,Fpatients."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
